regen.absent_element: confirmation mechanism for deleting project or removing work items
regen.new_specification: The system shall require user confirmation before permanently deleting a project or removing work items from a project to prevent accidental loss of information.
The current function specifications cover all aspects of the function description comprehensively. No new specification is needed.

regen.absent_element: system integrity in handling concurrent edits and project splits
regen.new_specification: The system shall maintain data integrity and consistency during the concurrent editing of projects and when projects are split into multiple segments, ensuring no data loss occurs.

label: The user shall be able to combine multiple projects into a master project.
absence: action of combining multiple projects into a master project
